  "title": "Business Development / Sales Engineer (Semiconductor Equipment) #76685",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Equipment Supplier</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Business Development / Sales Engineer (Semiconductor Equipment)</strong></li><li>Working Location: West – Jurong East (Walking distance to the company from MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days / Monday to Friday, 9am-6pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to SGD 5000 + Monthly Commission + AWS + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Drive sales of semiconductor equipment to meet and exceed sales targets</li><li>Collaborate with customers to evaluate systems, parts, and materials</li><li>Manage customer inquiries, RFQs, sales proposals, and quotation processes</li><li>Build and maintain strong customer relationships, understanding their needs and delivering tailored solutions to ensure long-term partnerships</li><li>Coordinate with customers and R&D on sales activities, including presentations, quotations, specification confirmations, negotiations, commissioning/acceptance, and post-sales support</li><li>Lead sales negotiations and ensure successful deal closures</li><li>Implement strategies to expand market share for assigned products and services</li><li>Prepare and submit sales reports for internal purposes</li><li>Respond promptly and efficiently to customer queries</li><li>Undertake any additional assignments as directed by management</li><li></li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. Diploma in Engineering</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office</li><li>Min. 1 year of sales experience, preferably experience in the semiconductor industry</li><li>Training is provided to inexperienced candidate</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#76685 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
